high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the counter, then hang a left and walk up to the end of the white table.
Pick up the closest metal fork off of the white table.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then hang a left and walk up to the oven and look up at the microwave
Open the rightmost cabinet door above the microwave and put the metal fork in the closest mug that is in the cabinet.
Take the mug with the fork in it out of the cabinet and close the cabinet door.
Walk back over to the white table where you got the fork.
Put the mug with the fork in it on the white table to the left of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a fork in it on a white table.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter ahead, turn left, move to the wall, turn left, face the table.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Turn left, bring the fork to the stove on the left.
Open the right cabinet above the microwave over the stove, put the fork in the mug in that cabinet.
Pick up the mug with fork in the cabinet.
Turn around, go back to the table, go to the other side of the table from before.
Put the mug with for on the table next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with fork on table.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the right side of the table
Pick up the fork on the table
Turn left then walk straight turn left on right side of the cabinet above the microwave
Open the cabinet then put in the fork in the mug
Pick up the mug with fork then close the cabinet
Turn left walk across the room walk straight on the left side of the table
Put the mug with fork on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with fork  on the table
